can never try suicide again, so they say.

1017
01:59:56,102 --> 01:59:58,152
Take care of yourself.

1018
02:00:00,628 --> 02:00:02,812
Leave me be.

1019
02:00:08,013 --> 02:00:11,162
My plan was to die with you...

1020
02:00:15,351 --> 02:00:21,842
But at the bitter end,
you called out my name.

1021
02:00:29,544 --> 02:00:34,069
I changed my mind... Mother.

1022
02:00:51,004 --> 02:00:52,935
See you around.

1023
02:00:52,970 --> 02:00:59,313
<i>I can't figure out why,
but what we want</i>

1024
02:00:59,704 --> 02:01:06,192
<i>is always surrounded by worries</i>

1025
02:01:06,528 --> 02:01:13,281
<i>Your halting habits</i>

1026
02:01:13,316 --> 02:01:20,263
<i>I thought were just mine</i>

1027
02:01:20,268 --> 02:01:25,608
<i>How foolish I was</i>

1028
02:01:26,449 --> 02:01:33,379
<i>After how long?
After how long?</i>

1029
02:01:33,414 --> 02:01:40,305
<i>A woman knows how to love</i>

1030
02:01:40,340 --> 02:01:46,987
<i>After how long?
After how long?</i>

1031
02:01:47,022 --> 02:01:54,231
<i>A man throws love away</i>

1032
02:01:54,511 --> 02:02:01,971
<i>Dreaming dreams inside a dream</i>

1033
02:02:02,447 --> 02:02:06,081
<i>and walking on</i>

1034
02:02:06,116 --> 02:02:08,114
How do you feel?

1035
02:02:12,659 --> 02:02:14,636
How's Makoto?

1036
02:02:22,182 --> 02:02:26,580
<i>Not just trying to impress him,</i>

1037
02:02:26,615 --> 02:02:32,260
<i>So many endearing things</i>

1038
02:02:27,754 --> 02:02:31,500
I'm sorry, Iwashimizu-kun.

1039
02:02:32,269 --> 02:02:38,633
<i>I want to fall in love</i>

1040
02:02:38,668 --> 02:02:45,554
<i>Don't know why you left me behind</i>

1041
02:02:39,649 --> 02:02:41,600
He's coming.

1042
02:02:43,740 --> 02:02:49,710
Taiga Makoto will come.
Scout's honour.

1043
02:02:45,564 --> 02:02:54,243
<i>I was arrogant and selfish</i>

1044
02:02:55,336 --> 02:03:02,491
<i>Without any light
With no end in sight</i>

1045
02:03:02,526 --> 02:03:09,367
<i>Me, knows how to love</i>

1046
02:03:09,402 --> 02:03:16,092
<i>Without any light
With no end in sight</i>

1047
02:03:16,127 --> 02:03:23,021
<i>You throw love away</i>

1048
02:03:23,889 --> 02:03:30,086
<i>Never focusing on the answers,</i>

1049
02:03:31,619 --> 02:03:35,459
<i>and drifting along</i>

1050
02:03:38,958 --> 02:03:41,677
<i>Innocent girl inside a mother</i>

1051
02:03:41,712 --> 02:03:44,802
<i>The wind unwrapping her hair</i>

1052
02:03:44,837 --> 02:03:49,485
<i>The first day he knew her name</i>

1053
02:03:52,505 --> 02:03:58,282
<i>Took a lifetime's worth of heartbeats</i>

1054
02:03:58,762 --> 02:04:03,937
<i>Speeding our love,
gentle at times</i>

1055
02:04:05,469 --> 02:04:11,612
<i>If that's your desire,
that I am with smiles</i>

1056
02:04:12,379 --> 02:04:16,685
<i>If you refuse, I'm in a fix</i>

1057
02:04:16,720 --> 02:04:19,319
<i>Dodging lies</i>

1058
02:04:19,354 --> 02:04:21,880
<i>A dying skyscraper</i>

1059
02:04:21,915 --> 02:04:25,756
<i>Sadness of a sky with no power lines</i>

1060
02:04:26,116 --> 02:04:30,277
<i>No need to cry about</i>

1061
02:04:32,457 --> 02:04:36,195
<i>Night or day, rain or sun</i>

1062
02:04:36,230 --> 02:04:39,234
<i>Autumn or winter,
spring or summer</i>

1063
02:04:39,269 --> 02:04:45,152
<i>All in a place where</i>

1064
02:04:45,582 --> 02:04:49,192
<i>Love and faith are in harmony</i>

1065
02:04:49,227 --> 02:04:54,901
<i>Ai and Makoto's fantasy</i>

1066
02:04:59,169 --> 02:05:05,940
<i>After how long?
