<i>Dreaming dreams inside a dream</i>

1071
02:05:35,070 --> 02:05:39,312
<i>and walking along</i>

1072
02:05:40,816 --> 02:05:47,747
<i>Finding love within love</i>

1073
02:05:48,745 --> 02:05:53,964
<i>and walking along</i>

1074
02:06:30,915 --> 02:06:33,374
You came for me.

1075
02:06:37,840 --> 02:06:41,908
I'm not fooling myself, right?

1076
02:07:55,151 --> 02:07:57,655
Hey, you.

1077
02:07:58,587 --> 02:08:01,246
You live in that big villa.

1078
02:08:08,649 --> 02:08:12,035
- I'm sorry.
- Don't cry.

1079
02:08:12,070 --> 02:08:15,412
What's your name?

1080
02:08:17,804 --> 02:08:20,523
I'm Saotome Ai.

1081
02:08:21,903 --> 02:08:26,394
- I'll carry you. - But...

1082
02:08:26,429 --> 02:08:31,752
If I knew you were rich,
I'd have punched you.

1083
02:08:44,488 --> 02:08:48,559
This is what the rich do.

1084
02:08:58,812 --> 02:09:02,613
Keep this a secret from now on.

1085
02:09:02,648 --> 02:09:06,820
It's uncool to get hurt saving a girl.

